-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This package (`@tegaki/dataset-cjk-kanjivg`) intentionally isolates KanjiVG
data in a dedicated workspace so that the CC-BY-SA 3.0 share-alike obligation
does NOT propagate to the main `tegaki` renderer or `tegaki-generator`
packages, which remain under the MIT License. Installing this package is an
explicit opt-in to the CC-BY-SA 3.0 terms for the dataset portion only.
